1
00:01:32,634 --> 00:01:34,010
Ada jurang.

2
00:01:34,344 --> 00:01:36,095
Jurang?

3
00:01:36,179 --> 00:01:39,098
Kedalamannya lebih dari cukup
untuk membunuh orang.

4
00:01:39,390 --> 00:01:41,684
Suster tak berbohong kepada kita

5
00:01:41,768 --> 00:01:43,978
dan iblis tak meremehkan kita.

6
00:01:44,479 --> 00:01:47,148
Jurang itu membuat pengamanan
tak dibutuhkan.

7
00:01:48,316 --> 00:01:50,652
Maksudmu, kita tak bisa kabur
dengan menyeberangi dinding?

8
00:01:50,735 --> 00:01:52,111
Tidak.

9
00:01:52,654 --> 00:01:53,905
Ada satu jalan.

10
00:01:59,911 --> 00:02:02,372
Jadi, aku berlari ke satu ujung dinding.

11
00:02:03,081 --> 00:02:04,916
Di sana, itu terbagi dua.

12
00:02:05,166 --> 00:02:07,168
Satu tetap pada jurang,

13
00:02:07,252 --> 00:02:09,963
satu lagi mengapit House ini.

14
00:02:10,839 --> 00:02:12,841
Mereka membentuk sudut sekitar 60 derajat.

15
00:02:12,924 --> 00:02:15,927
Kedua area di antara dinding

16
00:02:16,344 --> 00:02:18,680
cerminan satu sama lain.

17
00:02:20,765 --> 00:02:23,268
Pada dasarnya, Grace Field House ini

18
00:02:23,560 --> 00:02:28,147
terdiri dari enam area membentuk segi enam
yang dikelilingi jurang.

19
00:02:29,357 --> 00:02:32,610
Kita berada di pabrik tiga
dan area di sisi baratnya...

20
00:02:33,611 --> 00:02:35,864
Kemungkinan itu markas.

21
00:02:36,698 --> 00:02:39,075
Hanya ini yang memiliki jembatan.

22
00:02:39,576 --> 00:02:41,619
Mengingat adanya jurang,

23
00:02:41,995 --> 00:02:44,038
hanya ini rute pelarian kita.

24
00:02:46,791 --> 00:02:48,293
Norman!

25
00:02:48,710 --> 00:02:50,211
Kau dipanggil Ibu!

26
00:02:50,295 --> 00:02:51,713
Katakan padanya, aku segera datang.

27
00:02:51,796 --> 00:02:52,881
Baik!

28
00:02:56,426 --> 00:02:58,052
Baiklah, aku harus pergi.

29
00:02:58,136 --> 00:02:59,429
Tunggu!

30
00:02:59,512 --> 00:03:00,513
Norman!

31
00:03:00,597 --> 00:03:01,806
Kukembalikan ini.

32
00:03:02,098 --> 00:03:03,141
Belum kugunakan.

33
00:03:04,934 --> 00:03:06,019
Kau...

34
00:03:07,478 --> 00:03:10,148
Sejak awal, kau berencana untuk kembali?

35
00:03:10,648 --> 00:03:13,693
Bukankah katamu,
kau akan hidup dengan kami?

36
00:03:13,776 --> 00:03:14,903
Kalau begitu, kenapa?

37
00:03:15,153 --> 00:03:16,529
Apa sejak awal kau...

38
00:03:16,613 --> 00:03:18,948
Ya, aku berbohong. Maaf.

39
00:03:21,117 --> 00:03:25,955
Agar semua tetap hidup,
aku tak boleh melakukan kesalahan.

40
00:03:26,039 --> 00:03:28,041
Bila aku lari, rencana kita bisa kacau.

41
00:03:28,124 --> 00:03:30,543
Walau hanya berubah sedikit, tetap kacau.

42
00:03:30,877 --> 00:03:33,087
Tak boleh ada kesalahan.

43
00:03:33,838 --> 00:03:37,050
Jangan coba membujukku.
Tekadku takkan berubah.

44
00:03:46,100 --> 00:03:48,728
Aku telah melakukan semampuku hari ini.

45
00:03:50,021 --> 00:03:51,147
Sisanya kuserahkan padamu.

46
00:03:51,731 --> 00:03:53,399
Pastikan pelarian berhasil...

47
00:03:53,483 --> 00:03:54,943
Tunggu, Norman!

48
00:03:58,446 --> 00:03:59,489
Hangat sekali.

49
00:04:00,990 --> 00:04:02,408
Terima kasih untuk segalanya.

50
00:04:03,159 --> 00:04:05,453
Berkat kalian, hidupku berarti.

51
00:04:06,371 --> 00:04:07,580
Menyenangkan sekali.

52
00:04:08,623 --> 00:04:10,124
Aku bahagia.

53
00:04:10,667 --> 00:04:12,126
Aku benar-benar diberkati.

54
00:04:14,587 --> 00:04:15,546
Sial...

55
00:04:17,048 --> 00:04:18,174
Sial...

56
00:04:19,092 --> 00:04:20,385
Sialan!

57
00:04:21,886 --> 00:04:23,638
Dengar, Norman.

58
00:04:24,472 --> 00:04:26,516
Masih ada waktu. Larilah, ya?

59
00:04:26,599 --> 00:04:28,434
Kabur dan bersembunyilah di hutan.

60
00:04:32,105 --> 00:04:35,024
Sudah kubilang, tekadku takkan berubah.

61
00:04:38,027 --> 00:04:39,195
Selamat tinggal.

62
00:05:10,810 --> 00:05:12,228
Lagi-lagi demam?

63
00:05:12,687 --> 00:05:14,564
Tak ada perang bola salju untukmu, Tuan.

64
00:05:14,647 --> 00:05:15,732
Baiklah...

65
00:05:15,815 --> 00:05:17,817
DILARANG MASUK!

66
00:05:18,192 --> 00:05:20,319
Kami tak boleh bermain dengan Norman?

67
00:05:20,403 --> 00:05:22,071
Boleh, setelah dia sembuh.

68
00:05:22,155 --> 00:05:26,617
Jangan masuk ke UKS
untuk sementara. Kalian paham?

69
00:05:26,701 --> 00:05:28,369
Ya!

70
00:05:36,002 --> 00:05:37,045
Ba!

71
00:05:37,253 --> 00:05:38,212
Emma?

72
00:05:38,296 --> 00:05:39,630
Aku datang untuk bermain!

73
00:05:40,631 --> 00:05:42,842
Kenapa? Kata Ibu, tak boleh masuk.

74
00:05:42,925 --> 00:05:46,721
Tapi, Norman,
kau selalu sendirian ketika sakit.

75
00:05:46,804 --> 00:05:48,890
Kau pasti kesepian!

76
00:05:50,099 --> 00:05:53,311
Mari mengobrol. Aku yang akan bicara.

77
00:05:53,394 --> 00:05:55,980
Jangan. Kau bisa tertular.

78
00:05:56,064 --> 00:05:57,690
Tak akan.

79
00:05:57,774 --> 00:05:59,901
Ada yang bilang, aku tak mungkin demam.

80
00:06:01,235 --> 00:06:02,445
Apa? Emma?

81
00:06:03,154 --> 00:06:04,906
Kapan kau masuk?

82
00:06:05,156 --> 00:06:07,784
Bagaimana bila kau juga demam?

83
00:06:07,867 --> 00:06:10,328
Kata Ray tak apa-apa.

84
00:06:10,411 --> 00:06:11,287
Kata Ray?

85
00:06:11,370 --> 00:06:13,623
Di buku, orang bodoh tak demam.

86
00:06:16,375 --> 00:06:17,502
Tapi...

87
00:06:18,252 --> 00:06:22,048
Kau tak boleh di sini.
Menjauhlah dari UKS.

88
00:06:22,423 --> 00:06:23,633
Kau paham, Emma?

89
00:06:23,716 --> 00:06:24,967
Baiklah.

90
00:06:27,428 --> 00:06:28,805
DILARANG MASUK

91
00:06:46,405 --> 00:06:47,907
Aku datang!

92
00:06:49,992 --> 00:06:50,910
Kau tak boleh...

93
00:06:50,993 --> 00:06:52,912
Ini. Untukmu.

94
00:06:53,412 --> 00:06:54,539
Cangkir?

95
00:06:54,789 --> 00:06:56,290
Aku diajari Ray membuatnya.

96
00:06:56,374 --> 00:06:58,126
Emma!

97
00:06:58,292 --> 00:07:00,545
Astaga! Ibu tak bisa
membiarkanmu sedetik saja!

98
00:07:01,003 --> 00:07:03,548
Kita bisa menggunakannya untuk mengobrol!

99
00:07:08,886 --> 00:07:10,513
Halo?

100
00:07:11,013 --> 00:07:12,974
Bisa dengar aku, Norman?

101
00:07:16,144 --> 00:07:17,770
Ya, aku dengar.

102
00:07:18,396 --> 00:07:19,772
- Ray!
- Ya.

103
00:07:20,148 --> 00:07:23,609
Luar biasa! Kita bisa mengobrol
dari luar dengan ini!

104
00:07:23,693 --> 00:07:24,652
Hore!

105
00:07:24,735 --> 00:07:28,531
Bila kau bicara sekeras itu,
dia bisa dengar tanpa telepon.

106
00:07:28,614 --> 00:07:30,241
Benar juga.

107
00:07:57,101 --> 00:07:58,644
Aku siap, Ibu.

108
00:08:05,151 --> 00:08:07,653
Bagus. Ayo pergi, Norman.

109
00:08:08,404 --> 00:08:09,655
Semua telah menantimu.

110
00:08:09,739 --> 00:08:11,199
Bisa kita bertemu lagi?

111
00:08:12,158 --> 00:08:12,992
Norman...

112
00:08:13,075 --> 00:08:14,160
Jaga dirimu.

113
00:08:15,745 --> 00:08:17,205
Norman!

114
00:08:17,288 --> 00:08:19,123
Jangan menangis, Sherry.

115
00:08:19,207 --> 00:08:21,125
Lepaskan aku dengan senyuman.

116
00:08:21,375 --> 00:08:22,293
Kumohon?

117
00:08:22,835 --> 00:08:24,086
Baiklah!

118
00:08:24,170 --> 00:08:25,296
Norman...

119
00:08:25,379 --> 00:08:26,255
Phil.

120
00:08:26,839 --> 00:08:29,634
Gantikan aku membantu Emma, ya?

121
00:08:31,469 --> 00:08:32,470
Tentu.

122
00:08:36,140 --> 00:08:37,725
Emma, Ray di mana?

123
00:08:38,684 --> 00:08:39,936
Di UKS.

124
00:08:40,311 --> 00:08:42,855
Katanya, dia tak mau berpamitan.

125
00:08:42,939 --> 00:08:43,814
Begitu rupanya.

126
00:08:44,440 --> 00:08:46,150
Don, Gilda.

127
00:08:46,234 --> 00:08:48,069
Tolong jaga Emma dan Ray.

128
00:08:48,152 --> 00:08:50,238
Siap!

129
00:08:50,780 --> 00:08:51,656
Emma.

130
00:08:53,699 --> 00:08:55,409
Kuserahkan mereka kepadamu.

131
00:09:03,751 --> 00:09:05,836
Baiklah, semoga semua tetap sehat.

132
00:09:06,087 --> 00:09:07,547
Norman.

133
00:09:07,630 --> 00:09:08,965
Terima kasih untuk segalanya.

134
00:09:09,048 --> 00:09:09,882
Sampai jumpa.

135
00:09:09,966 --> 00:09:11,384
Jaga dirimu.

136
00:09:11,467 --> 00:09:13,135
- Sampai jumpa.
- Norman.

137
00:09:13,219 --> 00:09:14,178
Norman...

138
00:09:15,388 --> 00:09:16,597
Norman!

139
00:09:29,193 --> 00:09:30,069
Emma?

140
00:09:30,152 --> 00:09:31,529
Aku akan menyibukkan Ibu.

141
00:09:32,113 --> 00:09:33,739
Kumohon, larilah.

142
00:09:53,718 --> 00:09:54,594
Dasar bodoh!

143
00:09:54,677 --> 00:09:56,429
Kenapa kau begitu gegabah, Emma?

144
00:09:56,887 --> 00:09:58,514
Bukan ini yang seharusnya kau lakukan!

145
00:09:58,597 --> 00:09:59,432
Diam!

146
00:09:59,515 --> 00:10:00,391
Jangan pergi!

147
00:10:03,060 --> 00:10:04,353
Mereka bertengkar?

148
00:10:07,106 --> 00:10:09,275
Kenapa kau tak mengerti?

149
00:10:09,734 --> 00:10:12,737
Aku tak meminta semua ini!

150
00:10:12,820 --> 00:10:14,905
Aku hanya memintamu
melepasku dengan senyuman!

151
00:10:15,781 --> 00:10:17,241
Tolong lakukan itu untukku!

152
00:10:17,325 --> 00:10:20,453
Mustahil. Aku akan menghormati
semua keinginanmu, kecuali itu.

153
00:10:20,828 --> 00:10:22,955
Terutama bila di lubuk hatimu,
kau tak mau pergi!

154
00:10:31,589 --> 00:10:34,175
Kau gila.

155
00:10:34,592 --> 00:10:38,179
Bodoh, gegabah, naif, dan kekanak-kanakan,

156
00:10:38,721 --> 00:10:40,431
tapi begitu tegas.

157
00:10:40,973 --> 00:10:43,726
Karena itulah aku...

158
00:10:49,940 --> 00:10:51,859
Sudah waktunya, Norman.

159
00:10:53,736 --> 00:10:55,071
Baik, Ibu.

160
00:10:57,073 --> 00:10:58,282
Tunggu!

161
00:10:58,366 --> 00:11:00,409
Tenang, Emma.

162
00:11:00,493 --> 00:11:03,579
Aku tahu kau pasti sedih,
tapi berhenti bertingkah.

163
00:11:03,913 --> 00:11:06,248
Bila kau kembali mencoba,
akan kubunuh kau.

164
00:11:07,917 --> 00:11:09,335
Menyerahlah.

165
00:11:16,092 --> 00:11:17,551
Ibu, bolehkah?

166
00:11:18,427 --> 00:11:20,679
Aku ingin berpamitan pada Emma.

167
00:11:22,640 --> 00:11:24,475
Tentu saja. Silakan.

168
00:11:24,558 --> 00:11:25,935
Ayo, Emma.

169
00:11:35,319 --> 00:11:36,237
Emma.

170
00:11:36,821 --> 00:11:37,822
Ya?

171
00:11:37,905 --> 00:11:38,906
Terima kasih.

172
00:11:39,490 --> 00:11:40,324
Ya.

173
00:11:41,325 --> 00:11:42,743
Maaf telah membohongimu.

174
00:11:43,285 --> 00:11:44,161
Ya.

175
00:11:45,162 --> 00:11:47,248
Jangan cedera lagi, ya?

176
00:11:47,581 --> 00:11:48,624
Baik.

177
00:11:48,833 --> 00:11:50,418
Juga jangan gegabah.

178
00:11:50,918 --> 00:11:51,794
Baik...

179
00:11:52,253 --> 00:11:53,629
Makanlah yang teratur.

180
00:11:54,171 --> 00:11:55,005
Baik.

181
00:11:55,756 --> 00:11:56,841
Kuserahkan sisanya.

182
00:12:00,261 --> 00:12:01,137
Baik...

183
00:12:02,138 --> 00:12:04,932
Jangan khawatir.
Jangan pernah menyerah, ya?

184
00:12:08,060 --> 00:12:08,936
Baik.

185
00:12:27,830 --> 00:12:28,873
Emma!

186
00:12:40,009 --> 00:12:42,803
Kopermu kosong, 'kan?

187
00:12:42,887 --> 00:12:44,805
Ya, hampir.

188
00:12:45,264 --> 00:12:48,392
Karena apa pun yang kumasukkan,
takkan kubawa.

189
00:12:50,060 --> 00:12:54,899
Aku sudah menduga kau takkan kabur.

190
00:12:55,691 --> 00:12:58,444
Kau melakukan hal benar.
Aku bangga kepadamu.

191
00:12:58,527 --> 00:13:00,905
Kini, aku bisa mengirim Emma
dan Ray sesuai waktunya.

192
00:13:01,614 --> 00:13:05,659
Mereka akan "hidup bahagia
hingga takdirnya tiba"?

193
00:13:05,743 --> 00:13:08,662
Tepat sekali. Mereka akan hidup
penuh berkah.

194
00:13:11,207 --> 00:13:12,082
Tapi...

195
00:13:12,166 --> 00:13:13,918
Apakah kau bahagia?

196
00:13:18,005 --> 00:13:19,006
Ya.

197
00:13:20,925 --> 00:13:22,426
Aku sangat bahagia.

198
00:13:23,177 --> 00:13:25,471
Karena aku bisa bertemu denganmu.

199
00:13:53,415 --> 00:13:54,500
Kemarilah.

200
00:13:55,751 --> 00:13:57,962
Tunggu sebentar di sini.

201
00:14:24,989 --> 00:14:27,658
Selamat pagi, Anak-anakku tersayang.

202
00:14:28,367 --> 00:14:31,287
Ini hari baru dalam kehidupan
kalian 37 bersaudara.

203
00:14:31,537 --> 00:14:34,790
Mari bersyukur bahwa ini
hari yang bahagia, dan...

204
00:14:35,165 --> 00:14:36,667
Mari makan.

205
00:14:36,750 --> 00:14:39,128
Mari makan!

206
00:14:54,977 --> 00:14:55,853
Emma.

207
00:15:07,740 --> 00:15:10,326
Astaga! Jauh sekali terbangnya!

208
00:15:18,459 --> 00:15:20,294
Emma terlihat begitu sedih.

209
00:15:20,628 --> 00:15:22,796
Aku belum pernah melihatnya seperti itu.

210
00:15:22,880 --> 00:15:23,714
Ya...

211
00:15:23,797 --> 00:15:24,798
Benar juga.

212
00:15:25,049 --> 00:15:26,759
Bukan hanya Emma.

213
00:15:26,842 --> 00:15:28,052
Ray pun sama.

214
00:15:29,053 --> 00:15:31,597
Dia benar-benar murung.

215
00:15:32,389 --> 00:15:34,224
Mereka pasti merindukannya.

216
00:15:34,308 --> 00:15:37,645
Ya, mereka bertiga dekat sekali.

217
00:15:40,522 --> 00:15:42,733
Apa yang ingin kau bicarakan?

218
00:15:43,484 --> 00:15:45,945
Kita harus membuat rencana.

219
00:15:46,028 --> 00:15:47,404
Kita akan...

220
00:15:47,488 --> 00:15:48,447
Lupakan.

221
00:15:49,531 --> 00:15:51,951
Aku sudah tak peduli.
Mari mati saja di sini.

222
00:15:54,161 --> 00:15:57,081
Tak mungkin kabur.
Ada jurang di sekeliling

223
00:15:57,164 --> 00:15:59,583
dan jalannya hanya jembatan dari markas.

224
00:16:01,043 --> 00:16:02,586
Tapi yang terpenting, aku sudah muak.

225
00:16:03,879 --> 00:16:05,172
Aku sudah lelah.

226
00:16:10,844 --> 00:16:12,429
Lantas bagaimana dengan ini?

227
00:16:13,222 --> 00:16:15,975
Aku tak mau. Untukmu saja.

228
00:16:16,058 --> 00:16:17,559
Kaburlah jika kau mau.

229
00:16:17,643 --> 00:16:18,894
Tapi aku sudah tak mau.

230
00:16:21,146 --> 00:16:23,273
Maafkan aku, Emma.

231
00:16:27,027 --> 00:16:28,070
Emma?

232
00:16:33,450 --> 00:16:34,952
Ray, dasar kau...

233
00:16:35,035 --> 00:16:35,953
Maaf.

234
00:16:36,537 --> 00:16:39,373
Don, Gilda, aku minta maaf.

235
00:17:05,399 --> 00:17:07,151
Aku sudah mengetuk.

236
00:17:07,609 --> 00:17:08,902
Apa kau tak dengar?

237
00:17:11,780 --> 00:17:13,073
Kasihan sekali.

238
00:17:13,490 --> 00:17:15,951
Kau pasti sangat terluka.

239
00:17:16,410 --> 00:17:19,204
Norman tewas dan Ray kini hampa.

240
00:17:19,288 --> 00:17:21,540
Kau tak bisa melakukan apa pun sendirian.

241
00:17:22,249 --> 00:17:26,170
Kau sudah sangat putus asa.
Kini, kau takkan kabur.

242
00:17:29,131 --> 00:17:30,966
Menyerahlah.

243
00:17:31,341 --> 00:17:35,929
Cara terbaik menghindarinya
adalah menyerah pada takdir.

244
00:17:36,513 --> 00:17:40,517
Kau terluka karena berusaha melawannya.
Terimalah, maka kau akan tenang.

245
00:17:40,601 --> 00:17:41,435
Semudah itu.

246
00:17:46,315 --> 00:17:48,067
Emma, aku...

247
00:17:49,568 --> 00:17:55,574
Bila kau mau, aku ingin
memberikanmu prospek menjadi Ibu.

248
00:17:56,075 --> 00:17:57,868
Prospek menjadi Ibu?

249
00:17:57,951 --> 00:17:59,077
Benar.

250
00:17:59,161 --> 00:18:01,455
Kau akan tumbuh dewasa, punya anak,

251
00:18:01,538 --> 00:18:07,503
dan bila kemampuanmu diakui,
kau bisa kembali sebagai Ibu atau Suster.

252
00:18:07,586 --> 00:18:09,379
Kau punya semua kualifikasi
yang dibutuhkan.

253
00:18:09,922 --> 00:18:13,967
Bila kau menginginkannya,
aku akan merekomendasikanmu.

254
00:18:14,218 --> 00:18:17,805
"Siapa yang sudi"?
Itukah yang kau pikirkan?

255
00:18:19,389 --> 00:18:22,434
Kalau begitu, katakan, apa lagi
yang bisa kau lakukan?

256
00:18:22,810 --> 00:18:25,104
Sama sekali tak ada.
Tak ada yang bisa kau selamatkan.

257
00:18:25,187 --> 00:18:28,232
Kau akan terjebak dan mengutuk
kematian mereka dan kematianmu.

258
00:18:28,774 --> 00:18:30,818
Hiduplah dan bercita-citalah menjadi Ibu.

259
00:18:30,901 --> 00:18:33,779
Terima keputusasaanmu dan tenanglah.

260
00:18:36,031 --> 00:18:36,949
Tak mungkin.

261
00:18:37,574 --> 00:18:39,034
Apa pun kecuali itu.

262
00:18:41,662 --> 00:18:42,538
Baiklah.

263
00:18:42,996 --> 00:18:45,833
Berjuanglah sesukamu hingga mati.

264
00:18:46,542 --> 00:18:48,502
Kalian tak mungkin kabur.

265
00:18:49,002 --> 00:18:51,547
Kau akan mengetahui kenyataan yang pahit.

266
00:19:15,237 --> 00:19:16,947
Siap!

267
00:19:21,994 --> 00:19:23,704
Ini!

268
00:19:24,746 --> 00:19:26,123
Tunggu!

269
00:19:34,131 --> 00:19:35,549
Emma...

270
00:20:32,064 --> 00:20:32,940
Ray.

271
00:20:37,945 --> 00:20:40,155
Sedang apa kau di sini selarut ini?

272
00:20:41,990 --> 00:20:45,202
Berpamitan pada House.
Aku tak punya kesempatan lain.

273
00:20:45,535 --> 00:20:48,247
Besok ulang tahunmu, ya?

274
00:20:48,956 --> 00:20:51,708
Ya. Ini malam terakhirku.

275
00:20:52,376 --> 00:20:54,211
Besok aku harus pergi.

276
00:21:05,555 --> 00:21:06,765
Emma.

277
00:21:07,557 --> 00:21:10,185
Apa kau benar-benar menyerah?

278
00:21:12,145 --> 00:21:14,690
Aku tahu kau pasti tidak bisa menyerah,

279
00:21:15,399 --> 00:21:16,316
Emma.

